@startuml

title NovaDeploy — Deployment Sequence

actor Developer
participant "Git Repository" as Git
participant "CI Pipeline" as CI
participant "Container Registry" as Registry
participant "NovaDeploy API" as API
participant "Staging" as Staging
participant "Production" as Production

Developer -> Git : git push origin main
Git -> CI : trigger pipeline
CI -> CI : run tests
CI -> Registry : push image (sha: abc123)
Registry -> API : notify image ready
API -> Staging : deploy release v1.4.2
Staging --> API : health check passed
API --> Developer : ✅ Staging deploy complete

Developer -> API : promote to production
API -> Production : deploy release v1.4.2
Production --> API : health check passed
API --> Developer : ✅ Production deploy complete

@enduml
